<paragraph id="8BEF36A3FFD0FFF1A5F8FE431D31FDE1" blockId="32.[136,1452,158,581]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD0FFF1A5F8FE431F19FE74" bold="true" box="[189,294,410,436]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFD0FFF1A463FE431C74FE74" authorityName="Schauer" authorityYear="1847" box="[294,587,410,436]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Stachytarpheta" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="schottiana">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD0FFF1A463FE431C74FE74" box="[294,587,410,436]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Stachytarpheta schottiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be recognized by the elliptical leaves, attenuate base, decurrent, glabrous in both surfaces. It is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFD0FFF1A4B4FE661CACFE18" authorityName="Moldenke" authorityYear="1959" box="[497,659,447,473]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Stachytarpheta" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="restingensis">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD0FFF1A4B4FE661CACFE18" box="[497,659,447,473]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">S. restingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but can be differentiated by the presence of the bracts half the length of the calyx and corolla slightly exceeding the calyx (
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD0FFF1A7A6FE3A1CC5FE3C" box="[739,762,483,508]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">vs</emphasis>
. bracts exceeding the median portion of the calyx and showy corolla with twice the size of the calyx in 
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFD0FFF1A718FDDE1CC1FDE0" authorityName="Moldenke" authorityYear="1959" box="[605,766,519,545]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Stachytarpheta" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="restingensis">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFD0FFF1A718FDDE1CC1FDE0" box="[605,766,519,545]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">S. restingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
